CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Golden Heaven Group Holdings Ltd is an offshore holding company. Through the operating entities in China, It manages and operates six properties consisting of amusement parks, water parks, and complementary recreational facilities. The parks offer a broad selection of exhilarating and recreational experiences, including both thrilling and family-friendly rides, water attractions, gourmet festivals, circus performances, and high-tech facilities. The parks collectively contain nearly 159 rides and attractions. The firm's revenue is primarily generated from selling access to rides and attractions, charging fees for special event rentals, and collecting regular rental payments from commercial tenants.
